{"tid":327224,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"等腫瘤化驗結果真係好頂","createTime":"2017-07-18T14:51:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-19T16:05:49.000Z","uid":3560,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"575de5f50b298f919cbfdf26f95711c17b2f674d","tid":327224,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T14:51:12.000Z","msg":"好朋友突然斷左腳骨，發現原來骨入面有個腫瘤，所以啲骨好脆斷咗<br />\n而家床都落唔到，未知腫瘤良性定惡性又唔做得手術縛骨<br />\n已經訓左醫院個半星期等腫瘤化驗報告<br />\n又唔知幾時先有結果<br />\n係咁等真係好擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae3c62d31efb4fc136e9ac116307ec4585207a97","tid":327224,"uid":43959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T14:52:32.000Z","msg":"祝好運<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"376d234f5ca718c2edc6d55a61103ba217359181","tid":327224,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T14:52:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a2210cd6ba284723c043d61a09961f531a83e50a","tid":327224,"uid":7954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T14:53:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8601d3b7c62a2df59ff27c8497c17bb1e9aa90c7","tid":327224,"uid":3560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T14:56:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>腳骨都會有瘤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢病房全部都係骨瘤<br />\n有個好後生因爲個骨瘤喺背脊所以半身不遂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得廿幾歲咋嗰個病人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係好擔心，又唔知幾時有結果"},{"pid":"c597d34510690bc3851b20bdad1797d2401a38e5","tid":327224,"uid":3560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T14:58:31.000Z","msg":"等待真係好辛苦，最慘係唔知等幾耐<br />\n前兩日太無助，另外有位朋友帶左我去廟街占撘羅<br />\n代表佢健康嗰張卡，係惡魔正位的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0a82e37bc6256d6ba2c2d1c28e477162186da82","tid":327224,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T15:04:41.000Z","msg":"而家大小二便都要喺床上解決，長期扎實隻腳，涼無得沖頭無得洗，呢個狀態已經個幾禮拜"},{"pid":"f83ebfdee90e01ca3b6ded7b76609fbc024d438a","tid":327224,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T15:05:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 後生仔 瞓返兩三日乜都好啦"},{"pid":"bc993011e4372a9a56c4f5e225e6637d78d06a6a","tid":327224,"uid":3560,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T15:15:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 後生仔 瞓返兩三日乜都好啦</blockquote><br />\n腫瘤會自己好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  斷骨會自己埋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d18c8fa78c04c74e281140265b6072b3ffa5108","tid":327224,"uid":31015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T15:17:30.000Z","msg":"驗骨係耐d<br />\n正面d 加油"},{"pid":"44f4fad2e6886f2a912878f540a31d6b9b161364","tid":327224,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T15:22:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>驗骨係耐d<br />\n正面d 加油</blockquote><br />\n要幾耐架通常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccccf41a9232178fd7b60b855bbdc121cff5fbb7","tid":327224,"uid":2986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T15:31:01.000Z","msg":"有無痛"},{"pid":"395d02d38a749838